{"article_id":"amaUPzIJP3hCixsj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"New details emerged Friday night about the Santa Fe High School shooting suspect ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"who admitted to opening fire","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"and told","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"why he avoided shooting certain students ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"according to a probable cause affidavit and complaint","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"that identified charges against him .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"The suspect , Dimitrios Pagourtzis Jr. , 17 , was charged with capital murder of multiple persons and aggravated assault against a public servant ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"according to the document .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Pagourtzis \" surrendered \" to authorities","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"after coming out of an art classroom at the school ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"the document said ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"and was brought to the Santa Fe Police Department","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"where he was advised of","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"\" and later waived his Miranda Warning . \"","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"AFTER TEXAS SCHOOL SHOOTING LEAVES 10 DEAD ,","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"HUNT FOR EXPLOSIVES CONTINUES","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"The suspect was then interviewed","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"and `` he gave a statement","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"admitting to shooting multiple people inside \" the high school \" with the intent","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"on killing people , \"","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"the document said .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Pagourtzis also said","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"`` he did not shoot students","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"he did like","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"so he could have his story told , \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"according to the document .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Pagourtzis also said","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"he wore a trench coat","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"and carried a Remington 870 shotgun and a .38 caliber pistol ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"according to the document .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Hours after the deadly shooting","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"that left at least 10 people dead","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"unfolded ,","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"hundreds of mourners gathered for a vigil","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"held in honor of the victims .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"Among those in attendance were Dr. Leigh Wall , the superintendent of Santa Fe Independent School District , Sen. Ted Cruz and Gov . Greg Abbott .","depth":4},{"id":36,"text":"TEXAS SCHOOL SHOOTING SUSPECT DIMITRIOS PAGOURTZIS WORE ' BORN","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"TO KILL '","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"SHIRT ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"POSTED ABOUT GUNS ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"REPORT SAYS","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"\" No child , no parent , no student , no community should ever have to go through this again , \"","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Abbott said ,","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"adding","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"that he and the entire state were \" not here today and gone tomorrow , \"","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"but would remain","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"until \" normalcy , \" as well as \" safety is returned to your schools . \"","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"He also talked about his own experiences with challenges in life ,","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"speaking about the accident","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"that caused him to need a wheelchair .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"\" I know the anguish","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"so many families are facing today , \"","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Abbott said .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"\" What allowed me to rise up","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"from having my life broken in half ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"is the very same thing","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"that will repair and restore the fractured families today . \"","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Cruz took the podium ,","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"telling the crowd of people","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"that \" tonight , all of Texas is grieving . \"","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"\" None of us knows","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"why there ' s evil in the world , \"","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Cruz said .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"\" But this community has seen it -","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"has seen the face of unmitigated evil .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"Has seen the face of hatred","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"but let me encourage you ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"in spite of that evil ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"the community has also seen strength .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"This community has also seen love .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"This community has also seen courage . \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Every school in the Santa Fe Independent School District will be closed on Monday and Tuesday ,","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"according to a Facebook post from the district .","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"They added","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"that more school counselors and other resources will be available","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"because they know","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"\" students and staff are going to need counseling","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"to help them grieve \"","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"and \" need an outlet","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"to share their fears and concerns . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":159,"left":115,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":109,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":93,"right":108,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":93,"left":87,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":85,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":0,"right":84,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":82,"right":83,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,